Jaclyn Pfeiffer and Kelly Bardier were fired from Aloma Methodist Early Childhood Learning Center in Orange County . 
  The two have been together since October and worked at the same daycare for 18 months . 
  They say they were fired after the director of the daycare heard rumors about their relationship . 
  Aloma United Methodist Church says they were terminated for being gay . 
  The women are fighting to get their jobs back . 
 